snippet.title: Playthrough : Atari Jaguar - Kasumi Ninja
snippet.description: One of the 4 Jags fighting games (5  if you count Jaguar CD's Primal Rage) and I'd say its second best after Ultra Vortek.  (third if you count Primal Rage) You cant imagine how terrible those others are :) I beat Kasumi Ninja with hard difficulty to get the real ending. This is mostly a test video cause my usb  grabber is being uncooperative :(
